{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_13_03",
  "title": "小美山愛",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_mountain-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "このお祭り最大のイベントとは……これです！\nジャジャン！",
      "startTime": 4.5558382217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5.8000002861
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "お祭りのために飾り付けられた森を\n蔦を使って木から木へと移動する儀式だそうです！",
      "startTime": 8.6000002861,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10699.9997139,
          "startTime": 19.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.7666669528
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "早速私も木の上にいまーす！\n枝が大きくて余裕で立てます！　蔦もロープみたい！",
      "startTime": 16.1666669528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "さ、さすがに無茶振りが過ぎる……\n愛、やめるんだ。戻って来～い！",
      "startTime": 24.622026381,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.8926756542
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "この日のために私は体を鍛えてきたのかもしれません\nうなれ筋肉！　気合いを入れろ！　……行きます！！",
      "startTime": 31.922675864,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.0560089875
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.2926743825
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "オーー！！\nサンバ、サンバ、サンバーー……！！",
      "startTime": 37.5926743825,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 36.2926743825
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 36.2926743825
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1173.992284199997,
          "startTime": 37.4666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2181.3179016999984,
          "startTime": 38.4739922842
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3181.3179016999984,
          "startTime": 39.4739922842
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.3260092418
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "だからそれはサンバじゃないんだ、愛！\n戻って来～い！！",
      "startTime": 43.7922508567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.7838546754
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "はぁーー、楽しかった～～！\nこの村のお祭りは最初から最後まで刺激的でしたね！",
      "startTime": 51.9505213421,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.8505218507
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "私は特に、最後の儀式が燃えました！\n森と共に生きる人達の生活を全身で感じられましたよ",
      "startTime": 60.6171880087,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.4171885174
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "ロケがこれでおしまいなんて、残念です\nお祭りはこの後三日三晩続くというのに……！",
      "startTime": 69.0505213421,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ツアーの予定もあるからな。そこは我慢してくれ\n最後に、番組の視聴者向けのコメントを頼むよ",
      "startTime": 76.9000027974,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.5632907233
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました。このお祭りに参加して感じたことを\nお話しすればいいんですよね。……それじゃ行きます！",
      "startTime": 84.0428933428,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.8632902147
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "……世界には、私の常識では計り知れない文化があって\n実際に体験しないと、分からないこともあって……",
      "startTime": 94.8299568814,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "こうして一度、全く違う文化に触れられたこと\nそして、挑戦をやりきったことで自信がつきました",
      "startTime": 102.896623548,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.2966245653
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "これからもLizNoirとして、新しいことに挑んで\n目の前の壁をぶち壊していける、そんな自信が！",
      "startTime": 111.3872447053,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "村の人達と言葉は通じませんでしたが、笑顔と筋肉と\nそして一緒に踊ったおかげで、仲良くなれました！",
      "startTime": 120.3299553555,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10833.824808599986,
          "startTime": 131.1637801641
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.3299563727
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ、村のみなさんと最後のダンスをしてきます\nオーー！　サンバ、サンバ、サンバーー！！",
      "startTime": 128.7163792887,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.82995739
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "愛、本当にお疲れ様。良くやりきったな……\nサンバではなかったけど",
      "startTime": 139.9333361308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、ありがとうございます\n念願の番組に出られて、本当に楽しかったです！",
      "startTime": 145.4007282259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.7007221224
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "見事な体当たりだった。あんな過酷な撮影を\n笑顔でやり切るなんて……俺は今、感動しているよ……",
      "startTime": 153.6354763881,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "お、落ち着いて下さい\nまだ撮影は残ってるんですよ？",
      "startTime": 160.9205917997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.5539220813
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうだった、これから温泉施設に移動だったな\nミニコーナーの『世界の温泉突撃GO！』の撮影か",
      "startTime": 167.2666725159,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 171.5621983532
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03-ai017.m4a",
      "text": "どんな温泉か楽しみです！\n一緒に行きましょう、{user}さん",
      "startTime": 174.0622044567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_luxuryhotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "luxuryhotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 177.6455266003
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_luxuryhotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "luxuryhotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 177.6455266003
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03-ai018.m4a",
      "text": "『世界の温泉突撃GO！』、今回はこの温泉施設です！\n異国情緒が漂っていて……それに、凄く豪華ですね",
      "startTime": 184.3982138377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_luxuryhotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "luxuryhotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 190.262193267
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03-ai019.m4a",
      "text": "村は緑が多くて素敵でしたけど、車で一時間の所に\nこんな素敵な温泉施設があるなんて、ビックリです",
      "startTime": 195.2621993705,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_luxuryhotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "luxuryhotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 203.5621993705
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_03-ai020.m4a",
      "text": "では早速、温泉に突撃しようと思います！\n世界の温泉、突撃GO～！",
      "startTime": 203.5621993705,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_luxuryhotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "luxuryhotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 208.1955327038
